# Token pipeline ownership rules

## Files owned by Tokens Studio (never edit)
- src/tokens/tokens.json is written exclusively by the Tokens Studio Figma plugin.
- Never create, edit, rename, or delete token JSON in src/tokens/.
- If a token value looks wrong (a weight, a color, a font name), do NOT fix it
  here. Flag it to me and I will change it in the Tokens Studio plugin, which
  is the source of truth. A hand edit here will be silently overwritten by the
  plugin's next push.

## Generated files (never edit)
- dist/variables.css is generated by Style Dictionary (style-dictionary.config.js).
- Never edit it directly. To change output, change tokens.json (via the plugin)
  or the build config. Regenerate with: npm run build:tokens
- CI commits dist/variables.css after Tokens Studio pushes.

## Everything else
- Scripts, configs, and docs are owned by this editor. Edit freely.
- This package ships CSS only. Consumers use var(--ds-*) — never hardcode
  values that exist as tokens.
